{"tid":1357641,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「回回帶」ao爆料單野目前睇嚟係真","createTime":"2019-07-23T18:20:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T08:20:31.000Z","uid":8028,"like":66,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"64355e7fe965d7fd97d19a8b16fc5b61b8245398","tid":1357641,"uid":8028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:20:46.000Z","msg":"［回帶］AO內鬼洩漏政府部署<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1347972\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1347972</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n大家呢排係咁被分化 有人試圖不停帶風向<br />\n<br />\n元朗單野<br />\n<br />\n沙中線之前又有提過下<br />\n<br />\n我想講嘅係 大家一直都中緊計 明明ao提曬水 大家唔好再中計落去<br />\n<br />\n上環同元朗都要理，目標係對準政權。元朗單野細佬我認為可以將個foc轉返落政府嘅無能上 警黑合作市民生命安全完全唔可以再依靠現帶體系，唔好淨係focus曬係白衫人到 目標對返準個政權！<br />\n<br />\n然後再慢慢將取代現有體系嘅諗法輸出去唔同地方先可以升級。因為之前有post留言有巴打提過成立臨時政府大眾未必咁受呢套，以家我地要做嘅就係將呢個思想傳開去，咁先可以偏地開花。"},{"pid":"bb10a2c7ddef1018d3f7a2bdf5bba8502e559d39","tid":1357641,"uid":8028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:22:51.000Z","msg":"同埋點樣解決個批打手真係要諗諗"},{"pid":"96fa45009619a2580675988aa24a2afd47c487ee","tid":1357641,"uid":8028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:28:07.000Z","msg":"輸出輸出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18b74d4db821833803361a4e78c239536627ac33","tid":1357641,"uid":171643,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:28:25.000Z","msg":"中撚哂咁制"},{"pid":"8a33be303f38a03b8a573c9e0df9fc2ca0cf2ee9","tid":1357641,"uid":8028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:29:26.000Z","msg":"幫手推上去提下大家ao篇野呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a019ab58aca2a136abf3086c6172074b36262da","tid":1357641,"uid":8028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:32:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aa4eaef8db8acf913b9a8833d002d59628a0397","tid":1357641,"uid":111007,"like":1,"dislik